lead_paragraph: No chance Edmond Sumner could sleep in on his birthday, not with Xavier's Big East conference game set for an unusual 11 a.m. start time. Instead, the sophomore guard went out and rocked Georgetown with a performance that was anything but a snoozer.

headline.print_headline: Sumner's Career Day Leads No. 17 Xavier by Georgetown 81-76
